t/html/images/logo.html.ittf.contents:
svg
    $params color|#000, bgcolor|#fff, viewBox|0 0 660 280
	$
		var opt = {};
		opt.y0 = 10;
		opt.y1 = 10;
		opt.y1a = 90;
		opt.y2 = 210;
		opt.ybottom = 250;
        opt.color = color;

	$*
    width 660
	height 260
    *$
	preserve-aspect-ratio xMidYMid meet
    viewBox ${viewBox}
	rect
		x 0
		y 0
		width 660
		height 280
		fill ${bgcolor}
		stroke none
	
	polyline
		stroke ${color}
		fill ${color}
		stroke-width 2
		points 10 ${opt.ybottom}
			\b 45 ${opt.y0} 60 ${opt.y0} 75 ${opt.y1a + 40} 
			\b 120 ${opt.y2} 120 ${opt.y1a + 40} 
			\b 175 ${opt.y2} 175 ${opt.y1a + 20} 
			\b 230 ${opt.y2} 230 ${opt.ybottom}

	i( 250, &opt )
	zeta( 320, &opt )
	zeta( 450, &opt )
	i( 590, &opt )
	

	$*
	polyline
		stroke black
		fill white
		stroke-width 2
		points 62 60 62 56 78 ${opt.y1+4} 70 ${opt.y1+2} 70 ${opt.y1} 84 ${opt.y1} 84 60

	text Wizzi
		fill white
		font-family Georgia
		font-size ${y2}px
		font-weight bold
		x 20
		y 30
	text Factory
		fill white
		font-family Arial
		font-size 16px
		font-weight bold
		x 74
		y 46
	*$

t/html/layouts/empty_opt.html.ittf.contents:
$group
	$params &opt

    head 
		$if opt.title
			@title ${opt.title}
        meta 
            charset utf-8
        meta 
            name viewport
			content width=device-width, initial-scale=1

        link
            rel preconnect
            href https://fonts.googleapis.com
        link
            rel preconnect
            href https://fonts.gstatic.com 
            crossorigin
		$*
        link
			rel stylesheet
			href https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto
        *$
        link 
            @ rel "stylesheet"
            @ href "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/normalize.css@8.0.1/normalize.min.css"
		
		script
            module
                set window.__filename = 'browser'
                $if isWizziStudio && !opt.useFirebase
    				var WizziBrowser
    					{ 
    						@ log
    							function 
    								var line
    									_ Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments).map
    										function 
    											param argument
    											return 
    												iif typeof argument === 'string'
    													then argument
    													else JSON.stringify(argument)
    										._ join
    											@ '\n '
    								if arguments.length > 1 && arguments[arguments.length-1] === '-'
    								    set line += new Array(50).join('-')
    								set document.querySelector('#wizzi-browser-log').textContent += line + '\n'
    						@ clearLog
    							function 
    								set document.querySelector('#wizzi-browser-log').textContent = ''
    						@ setStatus
    							function 
    								param status
    								set document.querySelector('#wizzi-browser-status').textContent = status
    						@ setContent
    							function 
    								param newContent
    								var content = document.querySelector('#wizzi-browser-content')
    								while content.hasChildNodes()
    									_ content.removeChild(content.lastChild)
    								_ content.appendChild(newContent)
    			
		$hook head-styles-0
		$if isWizziStudio && !opt.useFirebase
    		@style
    			css
    				# wizzi-browser-status
    					margin .5em 0
    					font-style italic
    				# wizzi-browser-log
    					margin .5em 0
    					white-space pre-wrap
    				# wizzi-browser-content
    					margin .5em 0
    				# status:empty, #log:empty, #content:empty
    					display none
		./empty_styles( &opt )
		$hook head-styles
		$hook head-styles-2

    body 

		$hook

		$hook body-scripts-0
		$if isWizziStudio && !opt.useFirebase
    		div
    			# wizzi-browser-status
    			# wizzi-browser-log
    			# wizzi-browser-content
		./empty_scripts( &opt )
		$hook body-scripts
		$hook body-scripts-2
		$include html/scripts/meta

	$
		var react_dev_url = 'https://unpkg.com/react@latest/umd/react.development.js';
		var react_dom_dev_url = 'https://unpkg.com/react-dom@latest/umd/react-dom.development.js';

		var roboto_font_url = 'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500';
		var babel_url = 'https://unpkg.com/babel-standalone@6/babel.min.js'
		var mui_icons_url = 'https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons';

	head
		@title ${opt.title}
		meta
			charset utf-8
		meta
			name viewport
			content user-scalable=0, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width, height=device-height
        link 
            @ rel "stylesheet"
            @ href "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/normalize.css@8.0.1/normalize.min.css"

		./empty_styles( &opt )
	
	body
		# root

		$hook scripts-1

		./empty_scripts( &opt )

		
		$if !opt.mainJs

			script
				type text/babel
				module
					kind react
					$if opt.useMaterialUI
                        const ReactRouterDOM = window.ReactRouterDOM
                        const classnames = window.classNames
                        const

                                @ colors

                                @ fade
                                @ makeStyles
                                @ jssPreset
                                @ ThemeProvider
                                @ Container

                                @ withTheme
                                $if !opt.materialUI.v4
                                    @ Box
                                    @ Container
                                @ AppBar
                                @ Avatar
                                @ Backdrop
                                @ Badge
                                @ BottomNavigation
                                @ BottomNavigationAction
                                @ Button
                                @ ButtonBase
                                @ Card
                                @ CardActionArea
                                @ CardActions
                                @ CardContent
                                @ CardHeader
                                @ CardMedia
                                @ Checkbox
                                @ Chip
                                @ CircularProgress
                                @ ClickAwayListener
                                @ Collapse
                                @ CssBaseline
                                @ Dialog
                                @ DialogActions
                                @ DialogContent
                                @ DialogContentText
                                @ DialogTitle
                                @ Divider
                                @ Drawer
                                @ ExpansionPanel
                                @ ExpansionPanelActions
                                @ ExpansionPanelDetails
                                @ ExpansionPanelSummary
                                @ Fab
                                @ Fade
                                @ FilledInput
                                @ FormControl
                                @ FormControlLabel
                                @ FormGroup
                                @ FormHelperText
                                @ FormLabel
                                @ Grid
                                @ GridList
                                @ GridListTile
                                @ GridListTileBar
                                @ Grow
                                @ Hidden
                                @ Icon
                                @ IconButton
                                @ Input
                                @ InputAdornment
                                @ InputBase
                                @ InputLabel
                                @ LinearProgress
                                @ Link
                                @ List
                                @ ListItem
                                @ ListItemAvatar
                                @ ListItemIcon
                                @ ListItemSecondaryAction
                                @ ListItemText
                                @ ListSubheader
                                @ Menu
                                @ MenuItem
                                @ MenuList
                                @ MobileStepper
                                @ Modal
                                @ ModalManager
                                @ NativeSelect
                                @ NoSsr
                                @ OutlinedInput
                                @ Paper
                                @ Popover
                                @ Popper
                                @ Portal
                                @ Radio
                                @ RadioGroup
                                @ RootRef
                                @ Select
                                @ Slide
                                @ Snackbar
                                @ SnackbarContent
                                @ Step
                                @ StepButton
                                @ StepConnector
                                @ StepContent
                                @ StepIcon
                                @ StepLabel
                                @ Stepper

                                @ SwipeableDrawer
                                @ Switch

					$hook imports

					$if opt.useMaterialUI
						const theme

								{
									{ palette
										{ primary
											@ light colors.purple[300]

											@ dark colors.purple[700]

											@ dark colors.green[700]

					$hook components

					react App
						style

						$hook

					const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
                    $if opt.useMaterialUI

                            const StyledApp
                                _ withStyles
                                    @ styles
                                    $if opt.withTheme
                                        {
                                            @ withTheme true
                                    (
                                        @ App
                            log 'Calling root.render ThemeProvider+StyledApp'
                            _ root.render
                                < ThemeProvider 
                                    @ theme {theme}
                                    < CssBaseline 
                                    < StyledApp 
                        $else
                            log 'Calling root.render ThemeProvider'
                            _ root.render
                                < ThemeProvider 
                                    @ theme {theme}
                                    < CssBaseline 
                                    < App 
					$else
						log 'Calling root.render App'
                        _ root.render
							< App
							_ document.getElementById
								@ 'root'

		$hook scripts-2

t/html/layouts/site.html.ittf.contents:
$group
    $params &opt

    $
        opt.fonts = opt.fonts ? opt.fonts : [];
        opt.fonts.push({ 
            name: 'roboto'
            });
        var clazz = 'm-s color-header font-l font-w-xxl';
        var clazz2 = 'color-header font-x font-w-s';

    html/layouts/empty_opt( &opt )
        
        $append head-styles
            css /ittf/styles/reset.css.ittf
            css /ittf/styles/main.css.ittf
            css /ittf/styles/header.css.ittf
            $if opt.stickyNav
                style
                    # ${opt.stickyNav}.sticky
                        position fixed
                        top 0
                    . ${opt.stickyNav}OffsetMargin
                        padding-top ${opt.stickyNavOffset}px
        
        $hook head-styles

        $hook head-scripts
        
        . flex-row space-between bg-color-header color-header align-items-center
            id __main_navbar
            . flex-row
                html/a( , /, ${clazz2}
                    div
                        style width: 80px; margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;
                        html/images/logo(#efefef, #434343)
            . flex-row
                $if locals.user
                    $if opt.section != 'Starter'
                        html/a( Starter, /ittf/site/starter.html.ittf, ${clazz}
                    $if opt.section != 'Playground'
                        html/a( Playground, /ittf/site/playground.html.ittf, ${clazz}
                    $if opt.section != 'Productions'
                        html/a( Productions, /ittf/site/productions.html.ittf, ${clazz}
                    $if opt.section != 'Project'
                        html/a( Project, /ittf/site/project.html.ittf, ${clazz}
            . flex-row
                $if opt.section != 'Docs'
                    html/a( Docs, /ittf/site/docs.html.ittf, ${clazz}
            . flex-row m-r-x
                $if locals.user
                    html/a( Profile, /profile, ${clazz}
                    html/a( Log Out, /logout, ${clazz}
                $else
                    html/a( Log In, /login, ${clazz}
        
        $*
        div
            pre
                code
                    + ${_.inspect(loclazzls)}
        *$
        
        $hook

        $append body-scripts
            $if opt.stickyNav
                script
                    let header = document.getElementById("__main_navbar")
                    let stickyBar = document.getElementById("${opt.stickyNav}")
                    let stickyPos = stickyBar.getBoundingClientRect().top
                    _ window.addEventListener
                        @ "scroll"
                        => 
                            param e
                            let scrollPos = window.scrollY
                            log 'pre sticki', stickyPos, scrollPos, scrollPos > stickyPos
                            if scrollPos > stickyPos
                                _ stickyBar.classList.add('sticky')
                                _ header.classList.add('${opt.stickyNav}OffsetMargin')
                                log 'sticki', scrollPos
                            else
                                _ stickyBar.classList.remove('sticky')
                                _ header.classList.remove('${opt.stickyNav}OffsetMargin')

t/html/scripts/meta.html.ittf.contents:
$group
		
    script
        module
            _ document.addEventListener
                @ 'keydown'
                =>
                    param event
                    var keyName = event.key
                    if keyName === 'Control'
                        # do not alert when only Control key is pressed.
                        return

                    if event.ctrlKey && keyName === 'j'
                        set location.href= location.pathname + '?meta=json'
                        _ event.preventDefault
                        _ event.stopPropagation

                    if event.ctrlKey && keyName === 'h'
                        set location.href= location.pathname + '?meta=html'
                        _ event.preventDefault
                        _ event.stopPropagation
                        
                    if event.ctrlKey && keyName === 'b'
                        var i = location.pathname.lastIndexOf('/')
                        set location.href= location.pathname.substr(0, i) + '?meta=html'
                        _ event.preventDefault
                        _ event.stopPropagation						

                    if event.ctrlKey && keyName === 'e'
                        set location.href= '/ittf/docs/cheatsheets/index.html.ittf'
                        _ event.preventDefault
                        _ event.stopPropagation
